items.title: IndiGo co-founder sells $1.36 billion of airline's shares, term sheet shows
items.description: SYDNEY -The co-founder of Indian airline IndiGo, Rakesh Gangwal, sold a 5.7% stake in the low-cost carrier through a block deal worth about $1.36 billion, a term sheet showed on Tuesday. ...
